Program_Policies: Students in the Athletic Training Major are not permitted to obtain a Kinesiology Minor.; Students may need additional prerequisites to complete this minor.; A grade of C or better is required for all courses in the minor, as specified by Senate Policy 59-10. In addition, at least six credits of the minor must be unique from the prescribed courses required by a student's major(s).
